This a some helper scripts to manually get started with the reddwarf project.

Getting started:
1. Follow the README here: https://github.com/cp16net/reddwarf/tree/reddwarf%2Fmaster/integration
2. Copy or link these file to the directory: reddwarf / integration / vagrant / host
3. Start up nova: ./nova-start.sh
4. Source the platform.sh file: . platform.sh
5. Use the function as they are described in the file. 

Example: 
$ dbaas_login
 % Total    % Received % Xferd  Average Speed   Time    Time     Time  Current
                                Dload  Upload   Total   Spent    Left  Speed
 0     0    0     0    0     0      0      0 --:--:-- --:--:-- --:--:--     0
TOKEN = xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx2
$ 
